Package com.example.plannr.utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Chat
    This class links a chat id to the user name of the other user in the chat for displaying and server request purposes
    ChatAdapter
    This is an adapter for the recycler view that displays the individual messages in a chat
    ChatAdapter.ChatViewHolder
    This class defines the xml objects in the card view so that we can change their values
    ChatSelectionAdapter
    This is an adapter for the recycler view that displays the chats a user is in
    ChatSelectionAdapter.ChatSelectViewHolder  
    ChatSingle
    This class holds the messages in a chat and whether or not the signed in user sent the message.
    Const
    class that contains important urls for requests with backend to send and get info
    EventAdapter
    This is an adapter for the recycler view that displays the events a user is in
    EventAdapter.EventViewHolder
    This class defines the xml objects in the card view so that we can change their values
    Music
    This class manages the background music playing in the app
    Student  
    UserEvent
    class for UserEvent objects (really just event objects), with the given information
